    # fr "Anyway, thanks for the help!"
    fr "Bref, merci pour ton aide !"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:107
translate french mari13_5497b15e:

    # "Mari and I say our goodbyes and I leave. I wish I could have got that truck running for her."
    "Mari et moi nous disons au revoir et je pars. J'aurais aimé pouvoir remettre ce camion en état de marche pour elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:108
translate french mari13_a3af5f30:

    # "I'm not sure what to do at this point. Maybe I'll come across a solution later."
